events.name: アルマダ
events.note: アルマダはプライオリティ通常

parameters:
Explorer Armada: This must be the deepest part. But what is
that thing wandering around?

Mage Relm: It's something that isn't a living being... I
believe it exists beyond our understanding.

Thief Nora: There it is! I sensed a presence similar to a
moving statue!

Explorer Armada: To continue moving even after losing its
master for thousands of years, huh?

Explorer Armada: I feel a sense of astonishment and
melancholy at the same time.

Clea: I can see something like an accessory in a place like
a deep altar.
Clea: We should stay on guard.

Explorer Armada: I hope nothing happens, but I'll rely on
you.

Explorer Armada: There's no mistake... It's a square-shaped
accessory!

Priestess Sophia: It seems like nothing... is going to
happen, doesn't it?

Priestess Phoni: Yes, I don't hear any hostile voices. I
don't think anything is going to attack us.
Explorer Armada: Can we consider it as being trapped?

Mage Relm: It seems like we have no choice but to move
through the magic circle. I don't know where it leads to
though...

Explorer Armada: It seems like we have no choice but to go.
I'll go first, so please follow me.
